---
title: Easy Southern Beef Strips & Garlic Rice with Sweetcorn Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: A smokey aioli drizzled over beef strips will be the perfect thing to coax out those Louisiana flavours. Fragrant garlic rice gets
paired up with a charred corn and celery slaw for colour and crunch. The real magic begins when you get a bite of everything at
once!
